Ubuntu:
gsettings set org.gnome.nautilus.preferences always-use-location-entry true
gsettings set org.gnome.desktop.wm.preferences button-layout ":minimize,maximize,close"

*Arch installs*
sudo pacman -S perl-net-smtp-ssl perl-authen-sasl perl-mime-tools ctags gvim git tmux base-devel minicom xsel bat the_silver_searcher bat ripgrep unzip lrzsz uboot-tools
