*Fedora install*
sudo dnf install cmake tree git tmux tcputils ctags minicom gvim curl p7zip man-pages dtc python-pip flex bison astyle autoconf automake ncurses-devel uboot-tools ripgrep git-secret
sudo dnf module install bat

